room test_chamber {
name        "The Test Chamber"
description "A vast, white-tiled cube bathed in the sterile glow of a ceiling_light. A security_camera tracks your every move from the northwest corner. To the north, a heavy_door stands flush against the wall. A sleek terminal and a pedestal with a red_button occupy the center of the floor, while a glass_window looks out onto a darkened gallery."
short       "A sterile white testing room."
first_visit "The hum of air filtration is the only sound as the lights flicker to life. You are alone."
start       true
